722746f.title: Manhattan: Riverside Drive - 103rd Street
722746f.text:
310-311 Riverside Drive, at and adjoining the N.E. corner of
103rd Street.
About 1912.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.

722917f-b.title: Manhattan: 103rd Street - Riverside Drive
722917f-b.text:
Riverside Park: Three views photographed in a southwestward
direction from about 103rd Street. Nos. 2 and 3 show ships at anchor on
the Hudson River; several of which are U.S. Navy vessels.
Views 1 \& 2:- JJune 7, 1921.
View 3:- June 14, 1921.
Walter L. Bogert.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
